{"id":103141,"date":"2019-11-20T16:04:37","date_gmt":"2019-11-20T16:04:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/?p=103141"},"modified":"2019-11-20T16:04:37","modified_gmt":"2019-11-20T16:04:37","slug":"financial-commission-successfully-participated-in-finance-magnates-london-summit","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/2019\/11\/20\/financial-commission-successfully-participated-in-finance-magnates-london-summit\/","title":{"rendered":"Financial Commission Successfully Participated in Finance Magnates London Summit","gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"text"}]},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">November 20th, 2019, The Financial Commission today announces its successful participation in the<a href=\"https:\/\/events.financemagnates.com\/londonsummit2019\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> 2019 Finance Magnates London Summit<\/a>, which took place November 12-13th at Old Billingsgate in London, United Kingdom. We would like to thank all our trusted members, partners, attendees and exhibitors for making this year\u2019s conference one to remember.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.55.52.jpg\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-103132 size-600 alignnone\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.55.52-600x356.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"356\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.55.52-600x356.jpg 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.55.52-300x178.jpg 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.55.52-768x456.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.55.52-1024x608.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.55.52-200x119.jpg 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.55.52-400x238.jpg 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.55.52-800x475.jpg 800w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.55.52-1200x713.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.55.52.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Reinventing the Retail Broker Model<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<div style=\"width: 640px;\" class=\"wp-video\"><!--[if lt IE 9]><script>document.createElement('video');<\/script><![endif]-->\n<video class=\"wp-video-shortcode\" id=\"video-103141-1\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" autoplay preload=\"auto\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"video\/mp4\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.46.16.mp4?_=1\" \/><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.46.16.mp4\">https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.46.16.mp4<\/a><\/video><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">During the conference, our COO, Nikolai Isayev engaged in a fruitful discussion with other industry experts regarding the current state of the retail forex market and how brokers can adapt to the changes taking place in our industry now. Particular attention was devoted to regulations and licensing of brokers, as well as education, research and ultimately market pricing that customers receive. We would like to thank the panel for this informative discussion.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.49.21.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-103123\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.49.21-400x310.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"350\" height=\"271\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.49.21-400x310.jpg 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.49.21-300x232.jpg 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.49.21-768x595.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.49.21-200x155.jpg 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.49.21-600x465.jpg 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.49.21-800x620.jpg 800w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.49.21.jpg 1002w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" \/><\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.51.43.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-103114\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.51.43-400x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"355\" height=\"266\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.51.43-400x300.jpg 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.51.43-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.51.43-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.51.43-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.51.43-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.51.43-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.51.43-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.51.43-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/2019-11-20-18.51.43.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 355px) 100vw, 355px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">During the event our Chairman, Peter Tatarnikov and fellow representatives held meetings with our trusted broker members, as well as partners in fintech and legal services, exploring new opportunities to improve our industry and protect traders. Notably, we would like to congratulate our partners, Tradefora on their participation in the Summit Awards.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>The Future\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Commenting on the event, Chairman Peter Tatarnikov noted: \u201cThis annual event brings together all the best minds and ideas in our industry and this year has shown us that we have a great potential to improve and grow together as companies and as a community. I am delighted at the amount of interest we have received from brokerages, fintech providers and the general public in our services and our expertise in all matters related to retail Forex globally. We will continue to work with our members and partners to generate more value in 2020.\u201d<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Considering the feedback received at the conference we are confident that brokers will continue to choose the Financial Commission to handle not only their mediation and dispute resolution needs but other valuable services that have helped hundreds of brokers along the way.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We invite everyone interested to drop us a line at <a href=\"mailto:info@financialcommission.com.co\">info@financialcommission.com.co<\/a> to find out how the Financial Commission can help your business!<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>November 20th, 2019, The Financial Commission today announces its successful participation in the 2019 Finance Magnates London Summit, which took place November 12-13th at Old Billingsgate in London, United Kingdom. We would like to thank all our trusted members, partners, attendees and exhibitors for making this year\u2019s conference one to remember. Reinventing the Retail Broker [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"author":13,"featured_media":102702,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[14,12,15,16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-103141","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-commission-news","category-company-news-news-events","category-press-release","category-press-releases-news-events"],"acf":[],"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"link","format":"url"}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/103141","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/13"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=103141"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/103141\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/102702"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=103141"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=103141"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=103141"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}